<h1>CCAP - Online Assessment Training</h1>

<h4>Reminder! Please take this assessment seriously and answer the following truthfully</h4>

<div class="row">
    <div class="column">
        <p>6.) Which of the following are your largest Customer Groups</p>
        <input type="checkbox" id="Ornaments" name="Ornaments" value="Ornaments">
        <label for="Ornaments">Private/Consumers</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="Bags and Accessories" name="fav_language" value="CSS">
        <label for="css">Residential Interior Designers</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="javascript" name="" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="javascript">Galleries</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="javascript" name="" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="javascript">Commercial Interior Desiigners</label><br>
        <label for="others">Others:</label>
        <input type="text" id="others" name="others" value="">
        <br />
        <br />
        <p>7.) How much of you current business is from repeat customers?</p>
        <input type="checkbox" id="Ornaments" name="Ornaments" value="Ornaments">
        <label for="Ornaments">None</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="Bags and Accessories" name="fav_language" value="CSS">
        <label for="css">Some</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="javascript" name="" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="javascript">About Half</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="javascript" name="" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="javascript">Most</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="javascript" name="" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="javascript">All</label>

        <br />
        <br />
        <p>8.) List 3 main reasons why customers work with you as opposed to others?</p>
        <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Reason 1</label>
        <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
        <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Reason 2</label>
        <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
        <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Reason 3</label>
        <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
        <br />
        <br />
    </div>
    <div class="column">
        <p>9.) Are you looking to increase your sales?</p>
        <input type="radio" id="Ornaments" name="Ornaments" value="Ornaments">
        <label for="Ornaments">Yes</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="Bags and Accessories" name="fav_language" value="CSS">
        <label for="css">No</label><br>

        <br />
        <br />
        <p>10.) Biggest problem in gaining new customers? </p>
        <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Explain Below</label>
        <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
        <br />
        <br />
        <div class="form-group">
            <p style="color: darkred">Optional*</p>
            <label for="formFile" class="form-label mt-4">We would like to see a sample of your craft, please upload your work here.</label>
            <input class="form-control" type="file" id="formFile">
        </div>
        <br />
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="page1next"><a href="AssessmentResult" style="color:white">Submit</a></button>
    </div>



</div>
